People in the world cooperate based on the company, which naturally divides people into capitalists and employees, causing problems such as exploitation and oppression, economic crisis and so on. To solve this problem, can we achieve social division of labor and achieve fair benefits without relying on the company? So let's create a new world!
人们在世界上基于公司进行合作，这种合作方式天然的将人分为资本家和员工，造成了剥削和压迫、经济危机等等问题。为了解决这个问题，我们能否在不依赖公司的情况下完成社会分工协作，并取得公平的利益。让我们创造一个新世界吧！
